Type locality.
Canal de la Aguja, between Punta Aguja and Isla Aguja, Santa Marta area, Colombia , Caribbean Sea (
11 ° 18 ' 28 " N
;
74 ° 11 ' 32 " W
).

Distribution and ecology. Santa Marta , Colombia . It inhabits rocky shores and coral reefs, from 4–5 to 36 m ; usually quite abundant in the deeper reef areas near the city of Santa Marta , up to 2.1 % cover in transects at 17–22 m depth (
Zea 1994 b
).
